Dear 39,
Welcome! 10 years ago a dear friend told me “I told myself my 30s will be way better than my 20s” and ever since I’ve lived by and to that. So, as my last year in my 30s, you, 39, will be great! I have no doubt!
I can’t wait for all the adventures, the feelings, the smiles, the hugs, the tears and the dances. I can’t wait for another trip around the sun (and the world) lead by you. 39, I welcome you with open arms and excitement. I can’t wait to see what you have in store for me.
Cheers,
Me 🍾💖🥰
🎶I’ll be seeing you… in everything that’s light and gay🎶

Dear @petermonn 
Where to begin 🤔 I LOVE YOU. I love the way you see life. I love the way you treat others. I love how you’re an amazing dad to Boo. I love how you talk to him and care for him and play with him. I love how you’re true to how you are, your truth, your authentic self. I love your spirit and your connection to your spirituality. I love your sense of humor, how you laugh and make others laugh. I love how you love my family, your relationship with each of them, and how you want fix things you have no idea how to fix. I love you as my partner, my travel companion, my guide, my nurse, my emotional guru, and above it all, my husband. I promise to contribute to making this decade, and every decade, magical, memorable, amazing, beautiful and joyous! HAPPY BIRTHDAY Mr. Monn!
With infinite love,
Me!
PS Boobie says happy bday dad!

Querida madre,
Happy birthday to you!!! I love you so much 🥰 What an amazing journey of life you’ve had. Having the honor of being part of it has taught me that no goal is too big, that fears can be overcome, and kindness mixed with love opens every door. Thank you for all the lessons and the fun times! I know you will continue to dance through life with grace and excitement, and I can’t wait to dance along your side! Feliz cumpleaños madre querida!
TA,
Alex 👩‍👦

Dear anniversary,
You mark the official moment I chose to love @petermonn forever. Our journey has been a rollercoaster filled with accelerating high and traumatizing lows. Filled with laughter, dance, excitement, newness, darkness, cries, scares, and all kinds of thrills. Today, we choose to celebrate you as a day filled with immense gratitude, love and unity. I choose him everyday, I choose this ride everyday, I choose to love him everyday, I choose this journey everyday. So thank you, Anniversary, for this never ending ride. We are buckled in and excited for lifetime of excitement.
Cheers to you Anniversary, we love you!
- @petermonn & I

Dear San Diego,
I fell into your eyes the first time we met; but after this weekend, you now own my heart. You’re the place that will forever host the marriage of my baby brother, Juan, and beautiful sister-in-law, Jesi. You introduced me to the beautiful souls that traveled from all over to celebrate them, to support them, to love them, to choose them. You gave me beautiful memories with amazing friends. You gave my family magical memories and new experiences. And you expanded my family! Thank you San Diego for all the beautiful moments, tears of joy, dances, laughters and hugs! I look forward to the many more memories and can’t wait for my next visit!
With honor and love,
Daddy Paredes 💁🏽‍♂️
PS: Wish I could fit all the pictures in this one post!

Dear Christie,
Emotional support is an intentional verbal and nonverbal way to show care and affection for one another. And you my bestie are that and more! To me, and to so many. I’m so incredibly lucky to have you in my life, to have your support, your love, compassion, joy, beauty, brain, and all the fun things! You’re such an important part of my life and I’m honored to be part of yours. Today I celebrate you and the new amazing happy moments surrounding your heart.  Happiest of birthdays love! Let’s get extra cute and drink all the champs and espresso martinis our hearts desire 👯‍♀️
ILYSM,
Alex

Dear Fufu,
Your 20s gave you so much to celebrate, so much to learn from, so much to overcome, and a new chapter with so much to look forward to. This last decade gave you the tools to become an incredible brother, son, friend, and now husband. And although there is so much more your 30s will teach you, it’s time to sit back and enjoy the fruits of your hard work. I can’t wait to see all the things you will accomplish in your 30s and, most importantly, I can’t wait to continue to celebrate life with you! Happy 30th bday!
Love you,
Your big bro
